Later, I learned that when Hassabis had founded his company, DeepMind, back in 2010, fellow scientists had rolled their eyes, believing the construction of humanlike AI to be impossible. Almost every potential investor had turned Hassabis away, observing that enlightenment is not a business model.

💬 仅仅才过了十几年，AI 界就已经发生了翻天覆地的变化，从烫手的山芋变成了香饽饽。
